    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A boy in a raincoat finds himself by the river.<br>A black cat suddenly appears in front of him and challenges the boy to a fight.<br>Can the boy defeat all the cats?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simple combat with dice</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Damage to the cats is determined by the total value of the dice. <br>A specific dice combination will deal more damage!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrading with charms</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can buy charms with the coins you get by defeating cats. <br>The various effects of charms will help the boy.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stress-free game experience</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each game takes about 5 to 10 minutes. <br>The game is very simple so that you don't get tired. <br>Calm music, the sound of dice, and the cat's meow are waiting for you.</p>",
